// Sidebar
// Left navigation sidebar showing all items in the current session: diagrams,
// documents, designs, spreadsheets, snippets, and todos.
// Supports item selection, deletion, search filtering, grouped snippet display,
// and todo management.
// synced: 2026-03-26T14:00:05Z

filteredItems: merges all item types, deduplicates grouped snippets (one entry
per groupId using the group name), sorts by lastModified, then filters by
searchQuery.
Task graph entry is shown during implementation phases (execute-batch,
ready-to-implement, etc.).

FUNCTION Sidebar(onItemClick, onItemOpenNewTab, ...) -> JSX            EXPORT
  CALLS: ItemCard (ItemCard), AddTodoDialog (AddTodoDialog), useDataLoader (useDataLoader)
  Reads all item lists and selection state from sessionStore and uiStore.
  Renders: search input, task graph link (if in implementation phase),
  todo list, filtered item list.
  Shows AddTodoDialog when showAddTodoDialog is true.

---

FUNCTION handleDeleteItem(item) -> void
  Confirms with user. Calls appropriate api.delete* + store.remove* based on
  item.type.

---

FUNCTION handleItemClick(item) -> void
  CALLS: selectDiagramWithContent (useDataLoader), selectDocumentWithContent (useDataLoader),
         selectDesignWithContent (useDataLoader), selectSpreadsheetWithContent (useDataLoader)
  Routes to selectXxxWithContent for diagram/document/design/spreadsheet, or
  direct selectSnippet for snippets.

---

FUNCTION handleSearchChange(e) -> void
  Updates searchQuery state.

---

FUNCTION handleAddTodoConfirm(title, description) -> void
  Calls api.addTodo, storeAddTodo, then selectTodo with the new todo.

---

FUNCTION handleDeleteTodo(todo) -> void
  Calls api.removeTodo and storeRemoveTodo. Clears selection if deleted todo
  was selected.

---

FUNCTION handleSelectTodo(todo) -> void
  Selects the todo. Closes any todo dropdown.

---

FUNCTION isItemSelected(item) -> boolean
  Checks the appropriate selectedXxxId in the store against item.id.
